{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1063,"text":"I am a PhD student."},{"time":3794,"text":"And that means I have a question:"},{"time":5921,"text":"How can we make digital content graspable?"},{"time":9632,"text":"Because you see, on the one hand,\nthere is the digital world"},{"time":13209,"text":"and no question, many things\nare happening there right now."},{"time":16669,"text":"And for us humans, it's not quite\nmaterial, it's not really there --"},{"time":20119,"text":"it's virtual."},{"time":21754,"text":"On the other hand,"},{"time":23000,"text":"we're humans, we live in a physical world."},{"time":25110,"text":"It's rich, it tastes good,\nit feels good, it smells good."},{"time":28459,"text":"So the question is:"},{"time":29644,"text":"How do we get the stuff over\nfrom the digital into the physical?"},{"time":32720,"text":"That's my question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34310,"text":"If you look at the iPhone with its touch"},{"time":36460,"text":"and the Wii with its bodily activity,"},{"time":38461,"text":"you can see the tendency;\nit's getting physical."},{"time":41462,"text":"The question is: What's next?"},{"time":43969,"text":"Now, I have three options\nthat I would like to show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47016,"text":"The first one is mass."},{"time":49649,"text":"As humans, we are sensitive\nto where an object in our hand is heavy."},{"time":53264,"text":"So could we use that in mobile phones?"},{"time":56000,"text":"Let me show you\nthe weight-shifting mobile."},{"time":58509,"text":"It is a mobile phone-shaped box"},{"time":60242,"text":"that has an iron weight inside,\nwhich we can move around,"},{"time":63381,"text":"and you can feel where it's heavy."},{"time":65198,"text":"We shift the gravitational center of it."},{"time":68677,"text":"For example, we can augment\ndigital content with physical mass."},{"time":72773,"text":"So you move around the content\non the display,"},{"time":74973,"text":"but you can also feel where it is\njust from the weight of the device."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79488,"text":"Another thing it's good for is navigation."},{"time":82694,"text":"It can guide you around in a city."},{"time":84700,"text":"It can tell you by its weight,"},{"time":86391,"text":"\"OK, move right. Walk ahead.\nMake a left here.\""},{"time":89392,"text":"And the good thing about that is,"},{"time":91033,"text":"you don't have to look\nat the device all the time;"},{"time":93435,"text":"you have your eyes free to see the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95407,"text":"Now, mass is the first thing --"},{"time":96967,"text":"the second thing, that's shape."},{"time":99441,"text":"We're also sensitive to the shape\nof objects we have in our hands."},{"time":102819,"text":"So if I download an e-book\nand it has 20 pages --"},{"time":105379,"text":"well, they could be thin, right?"},{"time":106950,"text":"But if it has 500 pages,\nI want to feel that \"Harry Potter\" --"},{"time":109932,"text":"it's thick."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111118,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112148,"text":"So let me show you\nthe shape-changing mobile."},{"time":115000,"text":"Again, it's a mobile phone-shaped box,"},{"time":117000,"text":"and this one can change its shape."},{"time":121632,"text":"We can play with the shape itself."},{"time":123356,"text":"For example, it can be thin\nin your pocket,"},{"time":125429,"text":"which we of course want it to be."},{"time":127096,"text":"But then if you hold it in your hand,\nit can lean towards you, be thick."},{"time":130546,"text":"It's like tapered to the downside."},{"time":132547,"text":"If you change the grasp,\nit can adjust to that."},{"time":136236,"text":"It's also useful if you want to put it\ndown on your nightstand"},{"time":139282,"text":"to watch a movie or use as an alarm clock."},{"time":141350,"text":"It stands."},{"time":142535,"text":"It's fairly simple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"Another thing is,"},{"time":145715,"text":"sometimes we watch things\non a mobile phone"},{"time":147836,"text":"that are bigger than the phone itself."},{"time":149848,"text":"In that case -- like here, there's an app"},{"time":151882,"text":"that's bigger than the phone's screen --"},{"time":153819,"text":"the shape of the phone could tell you,"},{"time":155718,"text":"\"OK, off the screen, right here,\nthere is more content."},{"time":158340,"text":"You can't see it, but it's there.\""},{"time":159995,"text":"And you can feel it,\nbecause it's thicker at that edge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162817,"text":"The shape is the second thing."},{"time":165000,"text":"The third thing operates\non a different level."},{"time":168366,"text":"As humans, we are social, we are empathic,"},{"time":171387,"text":"and that's great."},{"time":173114,"text":"Wouldn't that be a way to make\nmobile phones more intuitive?"},{"time":176207,"text":"Think of a hamster in the pocket."},{"time":178088,"text":"Well, I can feel it, it's doing all right.\nI don't have to check it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181404,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":182454,"text":"Let me show you the living mobile phone."},{"time":184743,"text":"So, once again, a mobile phone-shaped box."},{"time":187295,"text":"But this one, it has\na breath and a heartbeat,"},{"time":190623,"text":"and it feels very organic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192469,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194785,"text":"And you can tell, it's relaxed right now."},{"time":197106,"text":"Oh, now -- missed call, a new call,"},{"time":199461,"text":"new girlfriend, maybe -- very exciting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201502,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203271,"text":"How do we calm it down?"},{"time":205317,"text":"You give it a pat behind the ears,"},{"time":208053,"text":"and everything is all right again."},{"time":210000,"text":"That's very intuitive,\nand that's what we want."},{"time":212697,"text":"So what we have seen are three ways\nto make the digital graspable for us."},{"time":216816,"text":"And I think making it physical\nis a good way to do that."},{"time":220001,"text":"What's behind that is a postulation,"},{"time":222533,"text":"namely, not that humans should get\nmuch more technical in the future;"},{"time":226793,"text":"rather than that, technology,\na bit more human."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}